OL,6,FTwo men drove around in the early
OL,7,Fhours looking for someone to rob
OL,8,Fbefore targeting a lone female student
OL,9,Fand threatening her with a hammer, a
OL,10,Fcourt has heard.
OL,12,FAshley Morrison and Benjamin McConway
OL,13,Fhad already picked up a sex worker on
OL,14,F18 January this year with the
OL,15,Fintention of robbing her before
OL,16,Fdeciding against their initial plan.
