OL,6,FInstead they spotted their victim as
OL,7,Fshe made her way back to her student
OL,8,Faccommodation, McConway jumped out of
OL,9,Fthe car from the passenger seat and
OL,10,Fshouted for her to empty her purse
OL,11,Fwhile raising a claw hammer above his
OL,12,Fhead.
OL,14,Fheard the woman, who was on the phone
OL,15,Fto her boyfriend at the time, put the
OL,16,Fbags and luggage she was carrying
OL,17,Fbetween herself and McConway. She said
OL,18,Fshe was on the phone before holding up
OL,19,Fthe mobile and telling the defendant
OL,20,Fhe was on camera.
