OL,6,FMcConway, who was wearing a hood over
OL,7,Fhis head and a snood to hide the
OL,8,Fbottom half of his face, jumped back
OL,9,Finto the car and the two men left the
OL,10,Fscene.
OL,12,FThe woman returned to her student
OL,13,Faccommodation and reported the
OL,14,Fincident to the night warden, later
OL,15,Falerting the .
OL,17,FDetails of the car were circulated to
OL,18,Fofficers and it was found in the Clase
OL,19,Farea of the city a few days later, on
OL,20,F21 January, after which it was taken
OL,21,Faway for forensic tests.
