OL,6,FHe told police it was Morrison who
OL,7,Ffirst suggested they should "mug"
OL,8,Fsomeone for the money to buy more
OL,9,Fdrugs. McConway said they later went
OL,10,Fout in the car "looking for someone to
OL,11,Frob."
