OL,4,Cwhile threatening her with hammer
OL,6,FIn the statement, the victim added she
OL,7,Fforgave the defendants, hoping they
OL,8,Fwould spend their time in prison to
OL,9,Freflect on their behaviour, and said
OL,10,Fshe wanted to be a doctor help people
OL,11,Fand contribute to society.
OL,13,FShe said she thought the men targeted
OL,14,Fher because they saw her as an easy
OL,15,Fand vulnerable target.
OL,17,FThe judge contrasted the victim's
OL,18,Fbravery and resolute character with
OL,19,Fthe "cowardly and bullying" defendants
OL,20,Fin the dock.
