OL,6,FAshley Morrison, aged 38, of Mysydd
OL,7,FRoad, Landore, Swansea, and 32-year-
OL,8,Fold Benjamin McConway, of Robert
OL,9,FStreet, Manselton, Swansea, both
OL,10,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to attempted
OL,11,Frobbery when they appeared in the dock
OL,12,Ffor sentencing. McConway had also
OL,13,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fpossession of an offensive weapon.
