OL,6,FDefending Morrison, who has four
OL,7,Fprevious convictions, Dan Griffiths
OL,8,Fsaid his client has depression and a
OL,9,Fdiagnosis of emotionally unstable
OL,10,Fpersonality disorder. Mr Griffiths
OL,11,Fsaid those issues were worsened by
OL,12,F"harmful levels" of alcohol and
OL,13,Fcocaine use.
OL,15,FHe said Morrison seemed genuinely
OL,16,Fmotivated to use the time he would
OL,17,Finevitably spend in productively.
